response.overview: A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster's moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.
response.tagline: You won't know the facts until you've seen the fiction.
response.title: Pulp Fiction
